{{Infobox Website | name = Angry Asian Man | favicon = | logo = Angry Asian Man.jpg | screenshot = | caption = | url = {{URL|blog.angryasianman.com|Blog.AngryAsianMan.com}} | commercial = | type = News | registration = | owner = [[Phil Yu]]<ref>{{cite news|title= Sex and the Asian man |work= [[The Los Angeles Times]]|date=|url= http://articles.latimes.com/2004/may/12/entertainment/et-pierson12|accessdate=2010-11-21}}</ref> | author = Phil Yu<ref>{{cite news|title=Mad Man: Meet Blogger Phil Yu |work=[[KoreAm]] |date= |url=http://iamkoream.com/angry-asian-man/ |accessdate=2011-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108013932/http://iamkoream.com/angry-asian-man/ |archivedate=2010-11-08 }}</ref> | launch date = 2001 | current status = Active | revenue = | slogan = }}
'''Angry Asian Man''' is an Internet [[blog]] founded in 2001 by [[Phil Yu]].<ref>{{cite news|title= Incensed And Empowered |work=[[Washington Post]] |date=2010-02-20|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/10/08/AR2005100801286.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://iamkoream.com/angry-asian-man/ |title=Meet Blogger Phil Yu |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016192611/http://iamkoream.com/angry-asian-man/ |archivedate=2012-10-16 }}</ref> The blog focuses on [[Asian American]] news, media, and politics. The [[Washington Post]] calls Angry Asian Man "a daily must-read for the media-savvy, socially conscious, pop-cultured Asian American."<ref>Jose Antonio Vargas, Incensed and Empowered, The Washington Post (Sunday, October 9, 2005), https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/10/08/AR2005100801286.html</ref> An accompanying podcast, entitled ''Sound and Fury: The Angry Asian Podcast,'' was launched in May 2012 and features interviews with Asian Americans.<ref>iTunes, Podcasts: Sound and Fury: The Angry Asian Podcast, https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/sound-fury-angry-asian-podcast/id525370224?mt=2</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedp.com/article/2011/03/angry_asian_man_stands_up_against_racism |title=The Daily Pennsylvanian :: 'Angry Asian Man' stands up against racism |publisher=Thedp.com |date=2011-03-18 |accessdate=2014-07-14}}</ref> [[File:KoreAm 2010-11 Cover.jpg|thumb|left|Founder Phil Yu on the cover of ''[[KoreAm]]'' November 2010]]
==Origins== Yu first began blogging with a personal website www.minsoolove.com in 2000. In April 2002, he registered for the URL www.angryasianman.com.
==Controversy== As of February 17, 2015, Yu is involved in a trademark and copyright infringement dispute with [[Lela Lee]] of [[Angry_Little_Asian_Girl,_Five_Angry_Episodes|Angry Little Asian Girl]].<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://blog.angryasianman.com/2015/02/i-am-being-threatened-with-angry-asian.html|title = I am being threatened with an Angry Asian Lawsuit|date = February 17, 2015|accessdate = February 17, 2015|website = Angry Asian Man|publisher = Blogger|last = Yu|first = Phil}}</ref> The dispute was recently made public on each of their respective blogs. Both parties have since removed their blog posts in regards to the subject after an intensifying response from the public. There appears to be no resolution at this time.
